{"tid":1030863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天氣速遞】冷鋒料今晚抵達　周日新界氣溫或跌至15度","createTime":"2019-02-21T09:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T16:50:05.000Z","uid":23120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e49ffd2342bab1e893ab82152342bf30c5764cc","tid":1030863,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"受溫暖潮濕的海洋氣流影響，本港近日早晚有霧。天文台預測，一道冷鋒將於今晚抵達廣東沿岸，本港未來數天會受東北季候風影響，天氣轉涼，風勢頗大及有雨，氣溫要到下周中期才逐步回升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，冷鋒會在今日稍後於廣東北部形成，並逐漸向南移動，預料今晚抵達沿岸，與其相關的東北季候風未來數天會影響沿岸地區。9天天氣預報顯示，氣溫會由今日的最高25度，跌至周日（24日）最低17度；自動分區天氣預報更顯示，周日新界多區氣溫或會降至15度。"},{"pid":"6ff2a5b3696c6cd82f033232bd7fc0287ef297cc","tid":1030863,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"撚狗天氣"},{"pid":"c6413bb81d91aef2fba7c78b873ea2d63b5c2f4a","tid":1030863,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"凍你就凍熱你就熱啦 唔好又凍又熱啦臭閪天文台"},{"pid":"3a08ef197891ef95a0bc6e99c4dec89d3850fd31","tid":1030863,"uid":14073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"如果我病左衛星都拆埋你，屌！"},{"pid":"cda73bfa390a6dd10ceadf8fa5b74c74e7514286","tid":1030863,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:14:50.000Z","msg":"做乜撚嘢呀 又凍又熱 玩撚殘人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9f30d49dc2e17c25295a7c1e9d7569f4e0de7e","tid":1030863,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />濕凍來了"},{"pid":"1d14eb8ce5dfb04927be982d8cab6c5e00b4964b","tid":1030863,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"點撚樣呀 又話過完冬天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl